pageContext.claim: “.@MayorBowser is grossly incompetent, and in no way qualified to be running an important city like Washington, D.C. If the great men and women of the National Guard didn’t step forward, she would have looked no better than her counterpart Mayor in Minneapolis!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump is wrong. A largely peaceful protest had formed outside the White House, which was broken up using forceful measures including gas in order for the president to take a photo in front of St. John's Episcopal Church.
